  "raw_meta_yaml": "context:\n  version: 2.0.2\n\npackage:\n  name: unitree-sdk2\n  version: ${{ version }}\n\nsource:\n  url: https://github.com/unitreerobotics/unitree_sdk2/archive/refs/tags/${{ version }}.zip\n  sha256: aa05c28463b9f3c9459efce19485a9777644b5671eb10908f9ae0de880e0b2cc\n  patches:\n    - add-sched-include.patch\n    - fix-destructors-cpp20.patch\n    - rename-vendored-dds-shlib.patch\n\nbuild:\n  number: 2\n  skip: not linux\n  script:\n    - if: x86_64\n      then:\n        - cd thirdparty/lib/x86_64\n    - if: aarch64\n      then:\n        - cd thirdparty/lib/aarch64\n    # Rename the vendored libraries to avoid conflicts with cyclonedds.\n    - patchelf --replace-needed libddsc.so.0 libddsc_unitree.so.0 libddscxx.so\n    - patchelf --set-soname libddsc_unitree.so libddsc.so\n    - patchelf --set-soname libddscxx_unitree.so libddscxx.so\n    - mv libddsc.so libddsc_unitree.so\n    - mv libddscxx.so libddscxx_unitree.so\n    - rm libddsc.so.0 libddscxx.so.0\n    - ln -s libddsc_unitree.so libddsc_unitree.so.0\n    - ln -s libddscxx_unitree.so libddscxx_unitree.so.0\n    # Build and install the SDK.\n    - cd -\n    - cmake -S . -B build/\n      -GNinja\n      -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release\n      -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=$PREFIX\n      -DBUILD_EXAMPLES=OFF\n      -DCMAKE_FIND_ROOT_PATH_MODE_LIBRARY=NEVER\n      -DCMAKE_POLICY_DEFAULT_CMP0109=NEW\n    - cmake --build build/ --target install\n\nrequirements:\n  build:\n    - ${{ stdlib('c') }}\n    - ${{ compiler('c') }}\n    - ${{ compiler('cxx') }}\n    - cmake\n    - ninja\n    - patchelf\n  host:\n  run:\n\ntests:\n  - script:\n      - cmake-package-check unitree_sdk2 --targets unitree_sdk2 ddsc ddscxx\n    requirements:\n      run:\n        - ${{ compiler('c') }}\n        - ${{ compiler('cxx') }}\n        - cmake-package-check\n  - script:\n      - echo \"Checking stdlib compatibility of installed shared libraries...\"\n      - export c_stdlib_version=${{ c_stdlib_version }}\n      - check-glibc lib/*.so* lib/*.a*\n    requirements:\n      run:\n        - cf-nvidia-tools\n  - script:\n      - ldd $PREFIX/lib/libddsc_unitree.so\n      - ldd $PREFIX/lib/libddscxx_unitree.so\n      - touch CMakeLists.txt\n      - echo \"cmake_minimum_required(VERSION 3.16)\" >> CMakeLists.txt\n      - echo \"project(unitree_examples CXX)\" >> CMakeLists.txt\n      - echo \"find_package(unitree_sdk2 CONFIG REQUIRED)\" >> CMakeLists.txt\n      - echo \"add_subdirectory(example)\" >> CMakeLists.txt\n      - cmake -S . -B build/ -GNinja -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release -DCMAKE_PREFIX_PATH=$PREFIX\n      - cmake --build build/\n    files:\n      source:\n        - example/\n    requirements:\n      run:\n        - ${{ compiler('c') }}\n        - ${{ compiler('cxx') }}\n        - cmake\n        - eigen\n        - ninja\n        - yaml-cpp\n\nabout:\n  homepage: https://support.unitree.com/home/zh/developer\n  license: BSD-3-Clause\n  license_file: LICENSE\n  repository: https://github.com/unitreerobotics/unitree_sdk2\n  summary: Unitree robot sdk version 2.\n\nextra:\n  recipe-maintainers:\n    - diegoferigo\n",
